      "filePath": "packages/antdv-next-pro/src/components/form/components/GroupedFieldAttrs/index.vue",
      "summary": "表单字段属性分组组件，将单个 Field 配置按职责分解为 gridItemProps、formItemProps、componentProps 和 formItemSlots 四组属性，通过作用域插槽传递给 FormItem 层消费。",
      "tags": ["form-component", "property-grouping", "slot-based", "vue-sfc"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "通过 Object.keys 遍历将未知属性按 gridItemPropKeys/formItemPropKeys 分类，未被归类的属性自动归入 componentProps，实现灵活的属性分流。"
    },
